FOR EVER AND ALWAYS AND ALL ETERNITY YOUR SHELAGH"Ž
╠Peter & Muriel Kenny
We wrote your name In the sand, but the waves washed it away
We wrote your name in the sky, but the clouds blew it away
So we wrote your name in our hearts and forever it will stay"č
