²In loving memory of our Mum & Dad
Leslie Victor Salt 22/09/1925 - 19/12/1993
Edna Salt 14/04/1932 - 03/08/2015
Every day, in some small way, memories of you come our way
Though absent, you are both ever near, still missed, still loved, and ever dear"é
 Marcus Egerton-Warburton (1994-2008)
If the purpose of life is to live it, to taste experlence to
the utmost, and to reach out eagerly and without
fear for newer and richer adventure, then
during a life that was far too brief you
proved yourself a
